<title>
Rear Floor Side Rear Member, Rear Floor Side Member Rear Reinforcement and Rear Floor Rear Panel (Partial) Removal and Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
The figure below shows condition where following parts are removed.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Front fender 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9A06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Back Panel 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B06017"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0170.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.926mm" ver = "02" gw = "227" gh = "122"/>
</figure>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06019001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Rear floor rear panel is to be reused.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06019002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Mark at the shown position and cut rear floor rear panel.
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
You may accidentally cut the parts under the rear floor rear panel when cutting the rear floor rear panel.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Take sufficient care not to damage the parts under the rear floor rear panel when cutting rear floor rear panel.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove rear floor rear panel.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60B9B0046.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "111.495mm" ver = "01" gw = "457" gh = "300"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
110 mm (4.33 in.) (Left side)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
100 mm (3.94 in.) (Right side)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Left side only
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove rear floor side rear member and rear floor side member rear reinforcement.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60B9B0047.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "197.118mm" ver = "01" gw = "434" gh = "542"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "3.411in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Grind welding spots using belt sander, if necessary.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06019003">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Before conducting any weld, check installation position and condition for installation part(s). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B04009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install rear floor side rear member and rear floor side member rear reinforcement.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld or plug weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60B9B0048.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "197.118mm" ver = "01" gw = "434" gh = "542"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install rear floor rear panel.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld or plug weld.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct continuous weld.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply anticorrosion wax to back side of continuous weld part.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60B9B0049.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "111.495mm" ver = "02" gw = "456" gh = "300"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
110 mm (4.33 in.) (Left side)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
100 mm (3.94 in.) (Right side)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Left side only
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
